{"data":[{"name":"104:1","price":"Woe to every backbiter and slanderer,","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ لِّكُلِّ هُمَزَةٖ لُّمَزَةٍ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6180,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"104:2","price":"who amasses wealth and counts it over and again[1],","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي جَمَعَ مَالٗا وَعَدَّدَهُۥ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6181,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1] Instead of spending in the way of Allah.","lang":"en"},{"name":"104:3","price":"thinking that his wealth will make him live forever.","arabic":"يَحۡسَبُ أَنَّ مَالَهُۥٓ أَخۡلَدَهُۥ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6182,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"104:4","price":"No indeed! He will surely be cast into the Crushing Fire[2],","arabic":"كَلَّاۖ لَيُنۢبَذَنَّ فِي ٱلۡحُطَمَةِ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6183,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[2] i.e., Hellfire, as it crushes and destroys all that is thrown in it.","lang":"en"},{"name":"104:5","price":"and how do you know what the Crushing Fire is?","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلۡحُطَمَةُ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6184,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"104:6","price":"It is the kindled Fire of Allah,","arabic":"نَارُ ٱللَّهِ ٱلۡمُوقَدَةُ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6185,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"104:7","price":"which reaches the hearts[3].","arabic":"ٱلَّتِي تَطَّلِعُ عَلَى ٱلۡأَفۡـِٔدَةِ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6186,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[3] Penetrating through bodies and reaching the hearts.","lang":"en"},{"name":"104:8","price":"It will be closed down upon them,","arabic":"إِنَّهَا عَلَيۡهِم مُّؤۡصَدَةٞ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6187,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"104:9","price":"locked with towering columns[4].","arabic":"فِي عَمَدٖ مُّمَدَّدَةِۭ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6188,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[4] i.e., columns of fire or columns of iron to which the inmates of Hell are chained.","lang":"en"}],"chapter":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah","Chapter Al-Humazah","Humazah","Surah Humazah","Chapter Humazah","Al Humazah","Surah Al Humazah","Chapter Al Humazah","Surah 104","Chapter 104","The Traducer","الهمزة"]}